{"tid":407901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"身體檢查醫生傻系？","createTime":"2017-09-20T19:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T22:48:07.000Z","uid":143080,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a4067c78f015de82021df299d548246f8ab5439d","tid":407901,"uid":143080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T19:42:42.000Z","msg":"今日同老婆兩個做身體檢查 <br />\n<br />\n醫生同我講我有不孕不育既情況 成個人灰哂 <br />\n<br />\n但出到去老婆好開心咁沖過黎話有左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n傻系醫生我咪有仔囉 乜撚樣不育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628b5abbbfbe35d3022d2681a122c286d3e2d9a4","tid":407901,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T19:44:02.000Z","msg":"係囉，應該係生左個仔之後先不育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeeaacbee2363738cd33679bbf04e4ff99905bda","tid":407901,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T19:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日同老婆兩個做身體檢查 <br />\n<br />\n醫生同我講我有不孕不育既情況 成個人灰哂 <br />\n<br />\n但出到去老婆好開心咁沖過黎話有左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n傻系醫生我咪有仔囉 乜撚樣不育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">樓主帽事既</span>"},{"pid":"a1c4e26bafc25ab8e145c08dfdf3a6d54007c4f3","tid":407901,"uid":20538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T19:49:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又真</span></span>"},{"pid":"77ce69e43c501bad9728a436af946a8736ebc1cb","tid":407901,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T19:51:39.000Z","msg":"兩者冇衝突，邏輯上可以並存<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">帽事嘅</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f034df48f67374d2240e4bb398aafc6bf10b5e","tid":407901,"uid":21782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T19:52:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">奇蹟囉</span>"},{"pid":"6b82ba57a4e3b94041e3a3ce5669a1b69c535fdd","tid":407901,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T19:53:45.000Z","msg":"醫生有無同你講故仔？<br />\n<br />\n一個八十歲的老人去做健康檢查。檢查途中，老人不斷向醫生炫耀他新婚的妻子多好多好。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;他才二十五歲！&rdquo;老人叫道，&ldquo;我們結婚四個月，你知道她對我有多忠誠，她無時無刻不需要我，粘我粘到我都感到厭煩了！&rdquo;&ldquo;而且，&rdquo;老人又說，&ldquo;告訴你，她最近懷孕了！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n醫生靜靜地聽著，一言不發，&ldquo;怎麼樣？&rdquo;老人得意洋洋地說，&ldquo;不錯罷？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n醫生抬起頭，看了他一眼。&ldquo;這讓我想起一位失散多年的朋友。他跟我說過一個故事，是他在非洲狩獵時遇上的事。當時他在草原上遇到一頭獅子，他立刻從背上抓下槍來瞄準。然而，他立刻發現他錯了，他拿到的是雨傘，不是槍。這時已經太遲，獅子正站在他面前，就要撲過來，他只好把雨傘扛在肩上，使盡吃奶的力氣&lsquo;砰砰砰&rsquo;大叫三聲，奇跡發生了，那獅子竟然倒下死掉啦。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;狗屎，這怎麼可能&rdquo;老人大叫，&ldquo;那一定是別人幹的！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我也這麼認為&rdquo;醫生說....."},{"pid":"2024ec3a2e581b61c4e577144a20866456264fbb","tid":407901,"uid":129810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T19:55:00.000Z","msg":"乜又係你 假膠confirmed <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befef683c3995960418606de223509b088cdef58","tid":407901,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T20:00:07.000Z","msg":"系你老母"},{"pid":"873cd3630905e68b5b617f5944c060ac704a001c","tid":407901,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T22:04:35.000Z","msg":"繼續吹"},{"pid":"b3abc2202880309467fcbae52baf812c837c101c","tid":407901,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T22:48:07.000Z","msg":"兩件事完全冇衝突喎。<br />\n<br />\nbtw恭喜先"}]}